title: Isekai no Senshi toshite Kuni ni Manekareta kedo, Kotowatte Heishi kara Hajimeru Koto ni Shita
altTitle: I Was Invited to Join the Country as an Otherworldly Warrior, but I Refused and Decided to Start as a Soldier
